9CThey%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20understand%20why%20anyone%20would%20build%20a%20mud%20house%20willingly%3B%20it%20was%20seen%20as%20something%20the%20poor%20do%20out%20of%20necessity.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEvery%20beam%2C%20every%20brick%20at%20Kosen%20Rufu%20Village%20Recluse%20holds%20a%20story%2C%20not%20just%20of%20resistance%20to%20mainstream%20tourism%2C%20but%20of%20radical%20care%20for%20the%20land.%20One%20person%20who%20oversaw%20this%20careful%20dance%20between%20terrain%20and%20technique%20was%20the%20chief%20architect%20Naresh%20Sharma%2C%20who%20worked%20closely%20with%20both%20the%20founders%20and%20Delia%20Kinzinger%20to%20bring%20the%20retreat%20to%20life.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FTBI-FEATURED-IMAGE-2025-07-11T183429.040-1752239969.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22No%20industrial%20material%20was%20used%20during%20the%20building%20of%20this%20sustainable%20home%20stay.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FTBI-FEATURED-IMAGE-2025-07-11T183429.040-1752239969.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FTBI-FEATURED-IMAGE-2025-07-11T183429.040-1752239969-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FTBI-FEATURED-IMAGE-2025-07-11T183429.040-1752239969-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FTBI-FEATURED-IMAGE-2025-07-11T183429.040-1752239969-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FTBI-FEATURED-IMAGE-2025-07-11T183429.040-1752239969-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-468167%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ENo%20industrial%20material%20was%20used%20during%20the%20building%20of%20this%20sustainable%20home%20stay.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20a%20copy-paste%20project%2C%E2%80%9D%20Naresh%20says.%20%E2%80%9CIn%20the%20mountains%2C%20you%20can%E2%80%99t%20force%20your%20ideas%20on%20the%20land.%20You%20have%20to%20read%20the%20slope%2C%20feel%20the%20weather%2C%20and%20understand%20how%20wind%20moves%20through%20the%20valley.%20Only%20then%20can%20you%20build%20something%20that%20lasts%2C%20not%20just%20physically%2C%20but%20spiritually%20too.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20time%20and%20tea%20heal%20most%20things.%20As%20the%20couple%20integrated%20with%20village%20life%2C%20attending%20weddings%2C%20sharing%20meals%2C%20and%20participating%20in%20festivals%2C%20their%20intentions%20became%20clearer.%20%E2%80%9CNow%2C%20we%E2%80%99re%20seen%20as%20part%20of%20the%20community%2C%E2%80%9D%20Manju%20says.%20%E2%80%9CAnd%20more%20importantly%2C%20the%20locals%20are%20starting%20to%20see%20value%20in%20their%20traditional%20homes%20again.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThat%2C%20perhaps%2C%20is%20the%20most%20lasting%20impact%20of%20Kosen%20Rufu%3B%20it%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20just%20welcome%20visitors%2C%20it%20encourages%20local%20preservation.%20The%20couple%20now%20advises%20villagers%20not%20to%20tear%20down%20their%20ancestral%20homes%20and%20is%20considering%20hosting%20community%20workshops%20on%20sustainable%20construction.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EA%20stay%20that%20teaches%20you%20to%20slow%20down%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20retreat%E2%80%99s%20name%2C%20%E2%80%98Kosen%20Rufu%E2%80%99%2C%20is%20a%20Japanese%20phrase%20meaning%20%E2%80%98peace%20and%20happiness%E2%80%99%20%E2%80%94%20a%20reflection%20of%20the%20couple%E2%80%99s%20Buddhist%20practice.%20True%20to%20its%20name%2C%20the%20homestay%20offers%20little%20by%20way%20of%20luxury%20as%20conventionally%20defined.%20There%20are%20no%20TVs%2C%20no%20a