travelers%20of%20today%20are%20a%20different%20breed%20from%20the%20checklist%20sightseers%20of%20yesterday.%3Cp%3ESingapore%20Institute%20of%20Directors%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EBanyan%20Group%20founder%20Kwon%20Ping%20Ho%20has%20spent%20over%2030%20years%20in%20the%20hospitality%20industry.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EHo's%20luxury%20hotel%20chain%20launched%20its%20first%20resort%20in%201994%20and%20now%20operates%20over%2090%20hotels%20globally.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EHo%20told%20BI%20that%20tourists%20today%20have%20vastly%20different%20expectations%20from%20their%20parents'%20generation.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fasia-hotel-mogul-hospitality-worst-industry-to-be-in-2025-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EKwon%20Ping%20Ho%3C%2Fa%3E%20has%20come%20a%20long%20way%20since%20he%20opened%20his%20first%20resort%20in%20Phuket%20in%201994.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHo's%20luxury%20hotel%20chain%2C%20Banyan%20Group%2C%20now%20operates%20over%2090%20hotels%20worldwide%2C%20including%20in%20countries%20like%20Cuba%20and%20Saudi%20Arabia.%20The%2072-year-old%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%20it's%20not%20just%20his%20company%20that's%20changed.%20His%20customers%20look%20much%20different%20than%20they%20did%20three%20decades%20ago%2C%20and%20they%20want%20different%20things%20out%20of%20travel.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20you%20talk%20about%20the%20people%20of%20my%20generation%2C%20when%20international%20travel%20just%20started%2C%20people%20were%20happy%20to%20go%20on%20group%20tours.%20They%20just%20go%20to%20a%20hotel%20and%20they%20eat%20in%20a%20hotel%2C%26quot%3B%20Ho%20said%20on%20the%20sidelines%20of%20the%20International%20Conference%20on%20Cohesive%20Societies%20held%20in%20Singapore%20last%20month.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBut%20young%20people%20today%20have%20long%20become%20jaded%20about%20international%20travel.%20They've%20been%20traveling%20with%20their%20parents%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%20%26quot%3BToday%2C%20when%20they're%20traveling%20on%20their%20own%2C%20they%20are%20looking%20much%20more%20for%20things%20that%20are%20out%20of%20the%20way.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHo%20said%20today's%20more%20seasoned%20travelers%20are%20a%20vastly%20different%20breed%20from%20yesterday's%20checklist%20sightseers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20are%20much%20more%20into%20experiences%2C%20and%20not%20just%20to%20see%20something%20beautiful%20because%20they've%20probably%20seen%20that%2C%20done%20that%20with%20their%20parents%20already.%20They%20are%20looking%20at%20experiences%20which%20are%20deeper%20and%20allow%20them%20to%20interact%20with%20the%20local%20community%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20continued.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHo%20isn't%20the%20only%20one%20who%20has%20noticed%20the%20generational%20shift%20taking%20place.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELast%20year%2C%20McKinsey%20surveyed%205%2C000%20travelers%20from%20China%2C%20Germany%2C%20the%20United%20Arab%20Emirates%2C%20the%20United%20Kingdom%2C%20and%20the%20US.%20The%20consultancy%20said%20that%2052%25%20of%20Gen%20Zers%20surveyed%20said%20they%20are%20willing%20to%20splurge%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftransformational-travel-experiential-luxury-safari-trends-2019-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Etravel%20experiences%3C%2Fa%3E%20compared%20to%2029%25%20of%20baby%20boomers%20surveyed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOne-size-fits-all%20tourism%20offerings%20of%20the%20past%20have%20grown%20outdated%26quot%3B%20as%20travelers%20seek%20%26quot%3Bcreative%20experiences%20that%20are%20tailored%20to%20their%20priorities%20and%20personal%20narratives%2C%26quot%3B%20McKinsey%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnother%20change%20Ho%20said%20he%20noticed%20was%20in%20the%20countries%20from%20which%20tourists%20tended%20to%20hail%20and%20the%20places%20that%20they%20chose%20to%20visit.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20I%20first%20started%20in%20hospitality%2030%20years%20ago%2C%20the%20nature%20of%20tourism%20was%20one%20direction%20and%20one%20color%2C%26quot%3B%20Ho%20said.%20%26quot%3BIt%20was%20basically%20white%20people%20from%20Europe%2C%20traveling%20in%20one%20direction%2C%20from%20west%20to%20east.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOver%20the%20years%2C%20what%20I%20call%20'rainbow%20tourism'%20has%20come%20up%20because%20of%20increasing%20wealth%20in%20other%20developing%20countries%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHo%20said%20this%20has%20led%20to%20a%20%26quot%3Bmulticolored%2C%20multifaceted%2C%20exciting%20tourism%20of%20people%20from%20all%20over%20the%20world%20traveling%20to%20all%20over%20the%20world.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou've%20got%20Indians%2C%20you've%20got%20Africans%2C%20you've%20got%20Arabs%2C%20you've%20got%20Chinese%2C%20and%20Japanese%2C%20and%20so%20on%2C%20and%20then%20of%20course%20you've%20got%20young%20people%20from%20within%20the%20region%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20continued.%20%26quot%3BThat%20to%20me%20has%20been%20the%20biggest%20change.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20January%2C%20UN%20Tourism's%20World%20Tourism%20Barometer%20said%20an%20estimated%201.4%20billion%20tourists%20traveled%20internationally%20in%202024%2C%20an%2011%25%20increase%20over%202023.%20UN%20Tourism%20said%20it%20expected%20international%20tourism%20arrival%20numbers%20to%20grow%20by%203%25%20to%205%25%20in%202025.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fluxury-hotelier-today-tourists-different-from-30-years-ago-2025-7%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1752451201000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F686e2b093d5881a51c1cf0f4%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fluxury-hotelier-today-tourists-different-from-30-years-ago-2025-7%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Kwon%20Ping%20Ho%2C%2072%2C%20said%20the%20backpacking%20travelers%20of%20today%20are%20a%20different%20breed%20f