s%20a%20business%20strategy%2C%20system%20design%2C%20or%20press%20release.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHuynh%20started%20at%20Amazon%20in%202006%2C%20only%20a%20few%20years%20after%20the%20company%20turned%20its%20first%20profit%20and%20while%20Jeff%20Bezos%20was%20at%20the%20helm.%20Bezos%20famously%20instilled%20this%20culture%20of%20memo-writing%20from%20the%20top%20down.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBezos%20insisted%20on%20dense%2C%20direct%20memos%20in%2010-point%20font.%20In%20his%202017%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.sec.gov%2FArchives%2Fedgar%2Fdata%2F1018724%2F000119312518121161%2Fd456916dex991.htm%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eletter%20to%20shareholders%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Bezos%20wrote%20that%20%26quot%3Bwe%20don't%20do%20PowerPoint%2C%26quot%3B%20instead%20opting%20for%20these%20six-pagers.%20%26quot%3BNot%20surprisingly%2C%20the%20quality%20of%20these%20memos%20varies%20widely%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBefore%20meetings%2C%20Amazon%20employees%20read%20these%20memos%20together.%20On%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DDcWqzZ3I2cY%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ELex%20Fridman%20Podcast%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%202023%2C%20Bezos%20explained%20why%20he%20didn't%20ask%20employees%20to%20read%20the%20memos%20in%20advance.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20problem%20is%20people%20don't%20have%20time%20to%20do%20that%2C%20and%20they%20end%20up%20coming%20to%20the%20meeting%20having%20only%20skimmed%20the%20memo%2C%20or%20maybe%20not%20read%20it%20at%20all%2C%26quot%3B%20Bezos%20said.%20%26quot%3BThey're%20also%20bluffing%20like%20they're%20in%20college%2C%20having%20pretended%20to%20do%20the%20reading.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAndy%20Jassy%2C%20Bezos'%20successor%20and%20Amazon's%20current%20CEO%2C%20has%20worked%20at%20the%20company%20since%201997.%20When%20first%20pitching%20what%20would%20become%20Amazon%20Web%20Services%2C%20Jassy%20described%20writing%20his%20own%20memo.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20remember%20this%20six-page%20narrative%2C%20we%20called%20it%20a%20vision%20doc.%20We%20asked%20for%2057%20people%2C%20which%20felt%20so%20ballsy%20at%20the%20time.%20I%20was%20so%20nervous%2C%20I%20wrote%2030%20drafts%20of%20this%20paper%2C%20and%20Jeff%20didn't%20blink%2C%26quot%3B%20Jassy%20said%20in%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DQVUqyOuNUB8%26t%3D244s%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E2017%20talk%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20the%20University%20of%20Washington.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJassy%20has%20continued%20the%20culture%20of%20memo-writing%20under%20his%20own%20leadership.%20In%20his%202024%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.aboutamazon.com%2Fnews%2Fcompany-news%2Famazon-ceo-andy-jassy-2024-letter-to-shareholders%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eletter%20to%20shareholders%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Jassy%20wrote%20that%20a%20mere%20six-page%20allotment%20made%20the%20memos%20%26quot%3Bmuch%20easier%20for%20the%20audience%20to%20engage%20with%20and%20ask%20the%20right%20'why'%20questions.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20got%20really%20really%20good%20at%20just%20reading%20these%20documents%20to%20get%20up%20to%20speed%2C%26quot%3B%20Huynh%20said%20on%20the%20podcast%2C%20explaining%20that%20reading%20enough%20six-page%20memos%20taught%20him%20to%20express%20himself%20in%20the%20same%20format.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHuynh%20no%20longer%20works%20at%20Amazon.%20He%20left%20to%20pursue%20YouTube%20content%20creation%20full-time%2C%20as%20he%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsalary-promotion-principal-software-engineer-amazon-quit-job-2024-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Etold%20BI%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%202024.%20But%20Huynh%20still%20reveres%20the%20company's%20reading%20culture%20%E2%80%94%20even%20if%20he%20acknowledges%20it%20may%20not%20be%20easily%20reproducible.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20difficulty%20would%20be%2C%20you%20actually%20have%20to%20be%20disciplined%20and%20principled%2C%26quot%3B%20Huynh%20said.%20His%20interviewer%2C%20Gergely%20Orosz%2C%20argued%20it%20could%20only%20be%20done%20from%20the%20top%20down.%20Huynh%20agreed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Famazon-engineer-6-page-memos-reading-culture-jeff-bezos-2025-7%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1752419829000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6873cae1f748d8c055f5868b%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Famazon-engineer-6-page-memos-reading-culture-jeff-bezos-2025-7%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Steve%20Huynh%20was%20a%20principal%20engineer%20at%20Amazon.%20He%20praised%20its%20culture%20of%20writing%20and%20reading%206-page%20memos%2C%20a%20practice%20that%20began%20under%20Jeff%20Bezos.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22hchandonnet%40insider.com%20(Henry%20Chandonnet)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A163%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Famazon-engineer-6-page-memos-reading-culture-jeff-bezos-2025-7%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%E2%80%98Beyond%20The%20Villa%E2%80%99%20Cast%20on%20Reuniting%2C%20Friendship%2C%20Feuds%20and%20Finding%20Love%20Outside%20of%20%E2%80%98Love%20Island%20USA%E2%80%99%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1752419700000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FBeyondtheVilla.jpeg%3Fw%3D1000%26h%3D563%26crop%3D1%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2F%3Fp%3D1236451577%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Season%206%20cast%20of%20%E2%80%9CLove%20Island%20USA%E2%80%9D%20is%20reuniting%20on-screen%20for%20the%20first%20time%20since%20leaving%20the%20villa%20in%20Fiji.%20%E2%80%9CLove%20Island%3A%20Beyond%20The%20Villa%E2%80%9D%20is%20a%20new%20spinoff%20from%20Peacock%E2%80%99s%20mega-hit%20reality%20dating%20show%20%E2%80%9CLove%20Island%20USA%2C%E2%80%9D%20which%20set%20to%20premiere%20on%20Sunday%2C%20J