%22%5C%22%3Eloans%20to%20pay%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStill%2C%20I%20wasn't%20satisfied.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20reclaim%20a%20sense%20of%20independence%2C%20I%20launched%20a%20house-call%20veterinary%20service%20around%20Chicago.%20It%20was%20just%20me%20and%20my%20wife%2C%20who%20helped%20out%20with%20scheduling%20and%20support.%20We%20provided%20high-end%2C%20in-home%20care%2C%20often%20euthanasia%20%E2%80%94%20helping%20pets%20pass%20peacefully%20under%20their%20favorite%20tree%20or%20on%20their%20family's%20couch.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20fulfilling%20and%20proved%20I%20could%20build%20something%20myself.%20But%20it%20wasn't%20scalable%2C%20and%20I%20was%20exhausted%2C%20juggling%20three%20vet%20jobs%20and%20always%20on%20call.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat's%20when%20I%20began%20to%20brainstorm%20product%20ideas.%20I%20didn't%20sleep%20much%20that%20year.%20I%20thought%20about%20everything%20from%20franchising%20the%20house-call%20model%20to%20launching%20new%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fpets%2Fbest-dog-supplement%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Epet%20supplements%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThen%20one%20day%2C%20a%20lightbulb%20went%20off.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22d27d0567-7342-4d58-b381-1736b5d0b935%5C%22%3EI%20saw%20the%20same%20problem%20again%20and%20again%20%E2%80%94%20and%20realized%20no%20one%20was%20solving%20it%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20a%20vet%2C%20I%20saw%20countless%20dogs%20with%20anal%20gland%20issues.%20They'd%20scoot%20across%20the%20carpet%2C%20sometimes%20rupture%20glands%2C%20and%20end%20up%20needing%20expensive%20surgery.%20The%20only%20solution%20we%20had%20was%20adding%20fiber%20to%20their%20diet%20%E2%80%94%20canned%20pumpkin%20or%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fpets%2Fbest-fresh-dog-food%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eprescription%20food%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20neither%20of%20which%20was%20very%20effective.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20client%20came%20in%20frustrated.%20He'd%20been%20back%20every%20three%20weeks%20for%20months.%20%26quot%3BIs%20there%20anything%20else%20we%20can%20do%3F%26quot%3B%20he%20asked.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20didn't%20have%20a%20good%20answer%2C%20and%20I%20hated%20that.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESo%20I%20went%20home%20and%20started%20researching.%20No%20product%20was%20on%20the%20market%20tailored%20specifically%20for%20this%20common%20condition%2C%20so%20that%20night%2C%20my%20idea%20for%20Glandex%20was%20born.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20created%20the%20formula%20myself%2C%20mixing%20soluble%20and%20insoluble%20fiber%20with%20other%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgut-friendly-high-protein-fiber-foods-doctor-stocks-kitchen-2025-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Egut-supportive%20ingredients%3C%2Fa%3E.%20I%20made%20the%20first%20batches%20in%20five-gallon%20Home%20Depot%20buckets%20in%20my%20basement.%20My%20wife%20and%20I%20packed%20and%20labeled%20everything%20by%20hand.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEventually%2C%20I%20launched%20Glandex%20online%20with%20a%20tongue-in-cheek%20campaign%3A%20%26quot%3BBoot%20the%20Scoot.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20wasn't%20an%20overnight%20success%2C%20but%20early%20Amazon%20reviews%20called%20it%20a%20miracle%20product.%20That%20was%20my%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftech-memo-vibe-coding-replit-create-app-review-test-limitations-2025-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eproof%20of%20concept%3C%2Fa%3E.%20We%20earned%20two%20patents%20and%20built%20the%20company%20%E2%80%94%20Vetnique%20%E2%80%94%20on%20the%20idea%20that%20science-backed%2C%20vet-formulated%20products%20could%20fill%20critical%20gaps%20in%20pet%20care.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20didn't%20have%20money%20for%20major%20ad%20campaigns%2C%20so%20I%20leaned%20into%20my%20network.%20I%20knew%20that%20if%20I%20could%20get%20veterinarians%20to%20recommend%20Glandex%2C%20it%20would%20spread%20faster%20%E2%80%94%20and%20more%20credibly%20%E2%80%94%20than%20any%20influencer%20campaign.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20sold%20directly%20to%20consumers%20and%20through%20Amazon%20and%20Chewy%2C%20but%20I%20also%20started%20building%20distributor%20partnerships%20and%20exhibiting%20at%20vet%20conferences.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20worked.%20By%202015%2C%20we%20were%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fholiday-gifts-pets-shopping-petco-petsmart-comparison-2021-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EPetSmart%20and%20Petco.%3C%2Fa%3E%20We%20expanded%20into%20grooming%20products%2C%20probiotics%2C%20and%20joint%20supplements.%20Slowly%2C%20I%20stopped%20practicing%20clinical%20vet%20med%20and%20went%20full-time%20at%20Vetnique%20in%202017.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22dfab8831-cd38-49f2-afe7-5577c7989f9b%5C%22%3EI%20sold%20the%20company%20in%20a%20multimillion-dollar%20deal%20%E2%80%94%20and%20stayed%20on%20to%20grow%20it%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIn%202023%2C%20I%20sold%20Vetnique%20to%20a%20private%20equity%20firm%2C%20Gryphon%2C%20in%20a%20multimillion-dollar%20deal.%20I%20still%20own%20about%2010%25%20of%20the%20company%20and%20remain%20CEO.%20We%20now%20have%20over%20200%20employees%20globally%2C%20including%20about%2055%20in%20the%20US.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESince%20the%20acquisition%2C%20we've%20doubled%20in%20size%20by%20acquiring%20UK-based%20pet%20supplement%20brand%20YuMOVE%2C%20entered%20Walmart%2C%20and%20expanded%20to%20over%2025%20countries.%20Our%20growth%20continues%20at%20over%2030%25%20year%20over%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOur%20mission%20is%20to%20help%20pets%20thrive%20for%20life%20by%20addressing%20the%20biggest%20health%20needs%3A%20digestive%20issues%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fpets%2Fbest-joint-supplements-for-dogs%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ejoint%20health%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20allergies%2C%20dental%20care%2C%20and%20ear%20care.%20But%20more%20than%20that%2C%20we%20aim%20to%20raise%20the%20bar%20in%20pet%20wellness%20by%20delivering%20science-based%2C%20vet-developed%20products%20that%20solv