%20Images%3B%20Tyler%20Le%2FBI%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EZombie%20funds%20are%20on%20the%20rise%20as%20private%20equity%20dealmaking%20and%20distributions%20slow.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EWe%20asked%20recruiters%20about%20the%20reputational%20impact%20of%20working%20at%20a%20zombie%20fund.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThey%20suggested%20looking%20for%20an%20exit%2C%20especially%20if%20you're%20an%20investor%20or%20fundraiser.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.tiktok.com%2F%40thedomthetroll%2Fvideo%2F7522567959533866253%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EHave%20you%20heard%20the%20news%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%3F%20A%20new%20contagion%20is%20turning%20formerly%20healthy%20private%20equity%20firms%20into%20the%20walking%20dead.%20It's%20not%20fungal%2C%20like%20in%20%26quot%3BThe%20Last%20of%20Us%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20virus%2C%20like%20in%20%26quot%3B28%20Days%20Later%2C%26quot%3B%20nor%20a%20magical%20reanimation%20like%20the%20original%20Haitian%20Vodou%20Zombis.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EInstead%2C%20it's%20the%20result%20of%20a%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwall-street-mergers-acquisitions-ipos-hiring-slumps-trump-tariffs-2025-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Edealmaking%20slump%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20pickier%20investors%2C%20and%20macroeconomic%20conditions%20that%20have%20turned%20some%20private-equity%20firms%20into%20glorified%20estate%20sales%2C%20auctioning%20off%20their%20dusty%20holdings%20before%20closing%20up%20shop.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThere%20are%20many%20definitions%20of%20a%20zombie%20fund%20%E2%80%94%20but%20no%20matter%20how%20you%20slice%20it%2C%20it%20can%20be%20bad%20for%20your%20career.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ETo%20some%2C%20a%20zombie%20fund%20is%20one%20that's%20passed%20its%20investment%20deadline%2C%20but%20is%20still%20holding%20onto%20capital%20to%20invest.%20Others%20say%20it's%20a