0foreseeable%20future%2C%20that%20is%20usually%20their%20sign%20to%20go%20straight%20to%20exploring%20the%20market%2C%26quot%3B%20Jessica%20Xu%2C%20head%20of%20investor%20relations%20recruiting%20at%20Selby%20Jennings%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%20is%20especially%20true%20for%20people%20in%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fprivate-equity-careers-fundraising-investor-relations-skills-experiences-jobs-2025-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Efundraising%20roles%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20where%20success%20means%20growing%20the%20firm's%20assets%20under%20management%20and%20building%20strong%20and%20deep%20relationships%20with%20investors.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBill%20Matthews%2C%20partner%20at%20BraddockMatthewsBarrett%2C%20said%20it's%20also%20true%20for%20people%20in%20investment%20roles%20because%20a%20zombie%20fund%20will%20drag%20down%20your%20investment%20track%20record.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%26quot%3BFolks%20have%20to%20pick%20their%20head%20up%20and%20move%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20adding%2C%20%26quot%3BOn%20the%20investment%20side%2C%20you%20want%20to%20have%20a%20track%20record%20of%20doing%20deals%20and%20exiting%20deals%2C%20and%20if%20there's%20a%20zombie%20fund%2C%20that's%20not%20going%20to%20be%20the%20case.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOf%20course%2C%20fundraising%20has%20slowed%20across%20the%20board%20and%20isn't%20necessarily%20a%20death%20knell.%20It's%20important%20to%20differentiate%20between%20a%20slowdown%20due%20to%20market%20conditions%20and%20one%20caused%20by%20dissatisfied%20investors.%20Just%20make%20sure%20you're%20keeping%20busy%20during%20the%20slowdown%2C%20said%20Lisa%20Steele%2C%20a%20partner%20at%20BraddockMatthewsBarrett.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%26quot%3BYou're%20maintaining%20relationships%20and%20keeping%20current%20LPs%20up%20to%20date%2C%20which%20is%20also%20critically%20important%20to%20these%20long-term%20partnerships%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said%2C%20referring%20to%20limited%20partners%2C%20the%20industry's%20catchphrase%20for%20fund%20investors.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EYou%20should%20also%20be%20developing%20new%20relationships%2C%20which%20Steele%20said%20will%20prove%20%26quot%3Bhugely%20valuable%20when%20you%20go%20back%20to%20market.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22071ac3a9-eac9-417d-90ed-d8b2eca42d10%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cstrong%3EHow%20to%20interview%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EA%20candidate%20running%20from%20a%20zombie%20fund%20may%20feel%20tempted%20to%20hide%20their%20current%20situation%20in%20a%20bid%20to%20make%20the%20candidacy%20more%20enticing.%20That%20would%20be%20a%20mistake%2C%20recruiters%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMatthews%20said%20hiring%20firms%20tend%20to%20know%20which%20of%20their%20peers%20are%20zombie%20funds%20from%20conversations%20with%20investors%20and%20other%20intermediaries.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20important%20for%20candidates%20to%20be%20as%20transparent%20as%20possible%20with%20potential%20employers%20about%20their%20reasons%20for%20wanting%20to%20leave%20their%20current%20firm%2C%20and%20working%20at%20a%20zombie%20fund%20is%20an%20understandable%20reason%2C%26quot%3B%20Xu%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20trick%20is%20to%20do%20it%20smartly.%20Recruiters%20warned%20against%20badmouthing%20the%20current%20employer%20or%20divulging%20confidential%20performance%20information.%20Focusing%20on%20personal%20gain%20is%20key%2C%20they%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%26quot%3BMany%20candidates%20in%20these%20situations%20feel%20constrained%20in%20their%20ability%20to%20drive%20growth%20and%20create%20meaningful%20value%20for%20their%20investors%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Xu%2C%20adding%20that%20they%20are%20%26quot%3Bseeking%20environments%20where%20they%20can%20contribute%20more%20strategically.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBy%20focusing%20on%20how%20you'd%20benefit%20from%20moving%20to%20a%20better-performing%20fund%2C%20you%20come%20across%20as%20a%20good%20player%20on%20a%20bad%20team.%20And%20it's%20worth%20remembering%20that%20there%20are%20worse%20situations%20to%20be%20in.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%26quot%3BA%20hiring%20firm's%20biggest%20fear%20is%20unknowingly%20hiring%20another%20firm's%20castoff%2C%26quot%3B%20Matthews%20said.%20%26quot%3BA%20zombie%20fund%20situation%20is%20obviously%20a%20good%20and%20valid%20reason%20why%20someone%20would%20want%20to%20leave.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fprivate-equity-zombie-funds-career-moves-interview-questions-solutions-2025-7%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1752406303000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F686d76d5f748d8c055f530bc%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fprivate-equity-zombie-funds-career-moves-interview-questions-solutions-2025-7%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20private%20equity%20slump%20means%20some%20firms%20are%20more%20walking%20dead%20than%20masters%20of%20the%20universe.%20Here's%20how%20to%20handle%20it%20if%20you're%20stuck%20at%20one.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22anicoll%40businessinsider.com%20(Alex%20Nicoll)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A18%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fprivate-equity-zombie-funds-career-moves-interview-questions-solutions-2025-7%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22South%20Korea%20medical%20students%20end%2017-month%20boycott%20of%20classes%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1752405962000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fichef.bbci.co.uk%2Fnews%2F1024%2Fbranded_news%2Fea8e%