table%20cultivation.%20The%20first%20vegetable%20she%20grew%20was%20a%20tomato%2C%20seeking%20help%20from%20an%20agricultural%20consultant%20to%20make%20the%20transition%20smooth.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ESoil%20health%2C%20raised%20beds%2C%20and%20a%20game-changing%20harvest%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20first%20focused%20on%20improving%20the%20soil%20health%20by%20adding%20cow%20dung%20and%20vermicompost.%20We%20just%20left%20the%20soil%20free%20for%20a%20few%20months%2C%20basking%20in%20the%20sunlight.%20We%20installed%20fences%20and%20ensured%20that%20the%20drainage%20system%20was%20in%20place%20and%20the%20land%20was%20sloping%2C%E2%80%9D%20Smarika%20shares%20with%20%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20also%20installed%20a%20drip%20irrigation%20system.%20After%20this%2C%20she%20prepared%20a%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F250491%2Fhow-to-grow-organic-tomatoes-up-woman-farmer-kanak-lata-success-story-him16%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eraised%20bed%20for%20tomatoes%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20mulch%20(a%20layer%20of%20material%20applied%20to%20the%20surface%20of%20an%20area%20of%20soil%20to%20conserve%20soil%20moisture%20and%20improve%20fertility).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20experimenting%20and%20researching%20over%20the%20weekends%20between%202019%20and%202021%2C%20Smarika%20took%20the%20plunge%20into%20full-time%20farming.%20With%20seeds%20purchased%20from%20a%20local%20nursery%2C%20the%20Chandrakar%20family%20prepared%20for%20their%20first%20tomato%20harvest%20in%202021.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201600px)%20100vw%2C%201600px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Fsmarika3-1719550058.jpeg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221600%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Smarika%20plans%20to%20ex