-standard.com%2Ftechnology%2Ftech-news%2Fcan-ai-improve-productivity-so-far-the-evidence-is-far-from-clear-125071300108_1.html%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22AI%20productivity%20increases%20can%20also%20sometimes%20be%20masked%20by%20additional%20human%20labour%20needed%20to%20train%20or%20operate%20AI%20systems%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Ftechnology%2Ftech-news%2Fcan-ai-improve-productivity-so-far-the-evidence-is-far-from-clear-125071300108_1.html%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22This%2027-YO%20Left%20Engineering%20to%20Build%20a%20Rs%2012%20Lakh-a-Month%20Zero-Waste%20Cafe%20That%E2%80%99s%20Changing%20How%20Kids%20Eat%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20used%20to%20hate%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F334569%2Fmillet-soups-drinks-for-winter-zomkom-rai-soup-bajra-ni-raab-ragi-halu-recipe%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eeating%20vegetables%20and%20millets%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%E2%80%9D%20admits%2010-year-old%20Jahnavi%20Nanda.%20%E2%80%9COnce%2C%20my%20mum%20gave%20me%20%3Cem%3Eragi%3C%2Fem%3E%20for%20dinner%2C%20and%20I%20was%20not%20very%20happy%20to%20eat%20it.%E2%80%9D%20Similarly%2C%20eight-year-old%20Kabir%20recalls%20his%20aversion%20to%20anything%20remotely%20healthy.%20%E2%80%9CI%20always%20thought%20healthy%20food%20tasted%20bland%20and%20boring%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says%20with%20a%20shy%20grin.%20%E2%80%9CI%20was%20far%20more%20interested%20in%20munching%20on%20crisps%20and%20chocolates%20during%20my%20meals.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20children%20growing%20up%20in%20an%20age%20of%20sugar-laden%20cereals%20and%20colourful%20packaging%2C%20the%20idea%20of%20eating%20for%20wellness%20rather%20than%20taste%20feels%20foreign.%20But%20a%20change%20is%20taking%20root%20in%20Gujarat%2C%20as%20more%20people%20begin%20to%20rediscover%20the%20value%20of%20ancient%20grains.%20Slowly%2C%20children%20are%20beginning%20to%20change%2C%20not%20just%20in%20what%20they%20choose%20to%20eat%2C%20but%20in%20how%20they%20think%20about%20food%20and%20the%20world%20around%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20centre%20of%20this%20change%20is%20a%20small%20cafe.%20It%20does%20not%20look%20extraordinary%20from%20the%20outside%2C%20but%20inside%2C%20it%20is%20helping%20to%20shape%20new%20habits%2C%20kinder%20choices%2C%20and%20a%20better%20understanding%20of%20where%20our%20food%20comes%20from.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EThe%20engineer%20who%20returned%20to%20her%20roots%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThat%20place%20is%20%E2%80%98Cafe%20Aarambh%E2%80%99%2C%20which%20means%20%E2%80%98beginning%E2%80%99%20in%20Hindi.%20It%20was%20founded%20by%2027-year-old%20Nishtha%20Chauhan%2C%20an%20electronics%20and%20communications%20engineer%20who%20left%20a%20promising%20career%20in%20aerospace%20to%20return%20to%20the%20earth%2C%20quite%20literally.%20Instead%20of%20the%20conventional%20corporate%20path%2C%20Nishtha%20chose%20to%20till%20the%20soil%2C%20grind%20millets%20and%20compost%20kitchen%20scraps.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHer%20journey%20is%20not%20a%20spontaneous%20detour.%20Raised%20in%20a%20modest%20Gujarati%20household%2C%20she%20grew%20up%20surrounded%20by%20the%20wisdom%20of%20her%20grandfather%2C%20a%20millet%20practitioner%20who%20firmly%20believed%20in%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F271562%2Fchennai-woman-sells-ready-to-eat-snack-mixes-from-ancient-grains%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Egoodness%20of%20ancient%20grains%3C%2Fa%3E%20like%20%3Cem%3Eragi%3C%2Fem%3E%20(finger%20millet)%2C%20%3Cem%3Ejowar%3C%2Fem%3E%20(sorghum)%2C%20%3Cem%3Ebajra%3C%2Fem%3E%20(pearl%20millet)%2C%20and%20little%20millet.%20Mealtimes%20at%20home%20were%20simple%20and%20wholesome.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20had%20grown%20up%20accustomed%20to%20seeing%20all%20the%20kitchen%E2%80%99s%20wet%20waste%20carefully%20composted.%20%E2%80%9CAt%20the%20time%2C%20I%20did%20not%20think%20much%20of%20it%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20tells%20%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E.%20%E2%80%9CBut%20once%20I%20became%20an%20adult%20and%20looked%20around%20me%2C%20I%20began%20to%20realise%20just%20how%20deeply%20those%20habits%20were%20ingrained%20in%20me%2C%20and%20how%20important%20they%20really%20are.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20graduating%20from%20Lalbhai%20Dalpatbhai%20College%20of%20Engineering%2C%20Nishtha%20joined%20Azista%20Aerospace%2C%20where%20she%20worked%20on%20satellite%20payloads%20in%20collaboration%20with%20the%20Indian%20Space%20Research%20Organisation%20(ISRO).%20It%20was%20an%20exciting%20work%20which%20was%20intellectually%20demanding%20and%20high-profile.%20But%20amid%20the%20sterile%20labs%20and%20long%20hours%2C%20she%20felt%20increasingly%20disconnected.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-07-11T092513.537_11zon-1752206127.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Nishtha%20Chauhan%20always%20wanted%20to%20start%20a%20food%20business%20but%20she%20was%20looking%20for%20something%20that%20can%20help%20the%20society%20and%20the%20environment%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-07-11T092513.537_11zon-1752206127.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-07-11T092513.537_11zon-1752206127-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-A