re%20conducted%20in%202024.%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBeed%2C%20situated%20in%20the%20heart%20of%20Marathwada%2C%20Maharashtra%2C%20faces%20significant%20challenges%20due%20to%20its%20arid%20landscape%20and%20ongoing%20water%20scarcity.%20With%20insufficient%20rainfall%20and%20a%20declining%20water%20table%2C%20agriculture%20in%20the%20region%20is%20a%20constant%20struggle%2C%20particularly%20for%20crops%20that%20require%20abundant%20water.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmid%20these%20difficulties%2C%20Parmeshwar%20Thorat%20has%20defied%20the%20odds%20by%20becoming%20a%20pioneer%20in%20avocado%20farming.%20%E2%80%9CI%20wanted%20to%20move%20away%20from%20traditional%20crops%20(like%C2%A0%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F301591%2Fhow-to-grow-pomegranate-at-home-in-pots-urban-gardener-shares-easy-tips%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epomegranates%3C%2Fa%3E)%20and%20try%20something%20unique%20and%20innovative%20%E2%80%94%20something%20no%20one%20else%20was%20doing%20in%20Beed%2C%E2%80%9D%20Parmeshwar%20tells%C2%A0%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20desire%20led%20him%20to%20explore%20the%20untapped%20potential%20of%20avocado%20farming.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAvocado%2C%20a%20fruit%20celebrated%20for%20its%20nutritious%20value%2C%20was%20relatively%20unknown%20in%20the%20Marathwada%20region.%20Its%20growing%20demand%20stems%20from%20its%20benefits%20for%C2%A0%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F292447%2Ffruits-that-reduce-blood-pressure-diet-for-heart-health%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emanaging%20blood%20pressure%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20diabetes%2C%20and%20heart%20health.%20%E2%80%9CI%20delved%20deep%20into%20research%20about%20the%20fruit%20and%20its%20advantages.%20I%20realised%20it%20could%20be%20a%20game-changer%20not%20just%20for%20my%20family%20but%20for%20the%20entire%20community%2C%E2%80%9D