ful%20avocado%20farmer%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20avocado%20saplings%20I%20planted%20have%20yet%20to%20bear%20fruit.%20In%20contrast%2C%20Parmeshwar%E2%80%99s%20farm%20is%20thriving%2C%20and%20he%E2%80%99s%20now%20successfully%20harvesting%20avocados!%E2%80%9D%20he%20remarks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ELeading%20by%20example%3A%20Educating%20the%20next%20generation%20farmers%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EParmeshwar%E2%80%99s%20journey%20into%20avocado%20farming%20is%20a%C2%A0%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F336695%2Finnovations-by-farmers-indian-agriculture-solar-dryer-biofertiliser-tree-scooter-organic-farming%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eremarkable%20story%20of%20innovation%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20resilience%2C%20and%20sustainable%20practices.%20What%20started%20with%20just%2050%20saplings%20on%20a%20small%20plot%20of%20land%20has%20now%20blossomed%20into%20a%20thriving%201.75-acre%20farm%20%E2%80%94%20home%20to%20300%20avocado%20trees.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CIn%202023%2C%20I%20harvested%20and%20sold%20around%201%2C200%20kg%20of%20avocados%2C%20earning%20a%20profit%20of%20Rs%205-6%20lakh%20after%20selling%20each%20fruit%20at%20Rs%20200.%E2%80%9D%20He%20mentions%20that%20maintaining%20the%20farm%20costs%20him%20about%20Rs%2050%2C000%20annually.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20addition%20to%20selling%20the%20fruit%2C%20he%20has%20also%20ventured%20into%20selling%20avocado%20saplings.%20In%202023%2C%20he%20sold%202%2C300%20saplings%20at%20Rs%20300%20each.%20After%20accounting%20for%20the%20cost%20of%20Rs%20100%20per%20sapling%2C%20he%20claims%20to%20have%20made%20a%20net%20profit%20of%20Rs%204.6%20lakh%20from%20sapling%20sales.%20In%20total%2C%20his%20net%20profit%20for%20the%20year%202023%20was%20approximately%20Rs%2010%20lakh%20per%20acre.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELooking%20ahead%2C%20Parmeshwar%20is%20determined%20to%20expand%20his%20business.%20%E2%80%9CI%20plan%20to%20supply%20my%20avocados%20to%20markets%20in%20Delhi%20and%20Mumbai%20next%20year%2C%20while%20continuing%20to%20sell%20in%20Beed%20and%20Pune%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FTBI-FEATURED-IMAGE-75_11zon-1752147727.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Grafting%20costs%20around%20Rs%20100%20per%20sapling%2C%20and%20in%202022%2C%20Parmeshwar%20grafted%20around%20250%20new%20saplings.%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FTBI-FEATURED-IMAGE-75_11zon-1752147727.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FTBI-FEATURED-IMAGE-75_11zon-1752147727-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FTBI-FEATURED-IMAGE-75_11zon-1752147727-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FTBI-FEATURED-IMAGE-75_11zon-1752147727-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FTBI-FEATURED-IMAGE-75_11zon-1752147727-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-467294%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EGrafting%20costs%20around%20Rs%20100%20per%20sapling%2C%20and%20in%202022%2C%20Parmeshwar%20grafted%20around%20250%20new%20saplings.%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEqually%20passionate%20about%20educating%20others%2C%20he%20adds%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20want%20to%20teach%20farmers%20how%20to%20grow%20avocados%20in%20drought-prone%20areas%20using%20drip%20irrigation%20and%20organic%20methods.%E2%80%9D%20Many%20farmers%20have%20already%20visited%20his%20farm%20to%20learn%20from%20his%20experience%2C%20