%20as%20a%20Flight%20Operations%20Inspector%20with%20the%20DGCA%2C%20Poonam%20helps%20keep%20flight%20operations%20across%20the%20country%20safe%20and%20accountable.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FTBI-FEATURED-IMAGE-66-1752129541.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FTBI-FEATURED-IMAGE-66-1752129541-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FTBI-FEATURED-IMAGE-66-1752129541-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FTBI-FEATURED-IMAGE-66-1752129541-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FTBI-FEATURED-IMAGE-66-1752129541-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-467009%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3ENow%20working%20as%20a%20Flight%20Operations%20Inspector%20with%20the%20DGCA%2C%20Poonam%20helps%20keep%20flight%20operations%20across%20the%20country%20safe%20and%20accountable.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20recounts%20to%20%3Cem%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E%2C%3C%2Fem%3E%20%E2%80%9CI%20was%20flying%20a%20flight%20from%20Doha%20when%20a%20cargo%20door%20alert%20forced%20me%20to%20reject%20takeoff%20just%20as%20the%20plane%20began%20to%20roll.%20Everything%20slowed%20down.%20I%20knew%20I%20had%20to%20act%20fast.%20I%20brought%20the%20plane%20to%20a%20halt%20and%20confirmed%20the%20issue.%20We%20were%20able%20to%20fix%20it%20and%20take%20off%20safely.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThat%20ability%20to%20stay%20calm%2C%20take%20charge%2C%20and%20keep%20people%20safe%20in%20high-pressure%20moments%20has%20shaped%20her%20journey%20ever%20since.%20She%20traces%20it%20back%20to%20those%20early%20years%20of%20training%20%E2%80%94%20the%20long%20hours%2C%20the%20drills%2C%C2%A0%20and%20the%20discipline%20it%20taught%20her.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEven%20when%20Jet%20Airways%20was%20nearing%20closure%20in%202019%2C%20she%20stood%20by%20it.%20%E2%80%9CI%20flew%20empty%20aircraft%20and%20worked%20unpaid%20for%20months.%20Jet%20had%20given%20me%20so%20much.%20I%20felt%20it%20was%20my%20duty%20to%20give%20back%2C%20right%20till%20the%20end.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENow%20working%20as%20a%20Flight%20Operations%20Inspector%20with%20the%20DGCA%2C%20Poonam%20helps%20keep%20flight%20operations%20across%20the%20country%20safe%20and%20accountable.%20It%E2%80%99s%20a%20role%20that%20brings%20together%20everything%20she%E2%80%99s%20learned%20%E2%80%94%20her%20years%20in%20the%20cockpit%20and%20her%20studies%20in%20aviation%20law%20and%20airline%20management.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMy%20work%20now%20is%20about%20setting%20and%20maintaining%20the%20highest%20safety%20standards%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%20%E2%80%9CEvery%20audit%2C%20every%20training%20review%20%E2%80%94%20it%20all%20comes%20down%20to%20one%20thing%3A%20keeping%20our%20skies%20safe.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EInside%20a%20pilot%E2%80%99s%20mind%20during%20a%20mid-air%20emergency%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20safety%20concerns%20have%20been%20a%20recent%20topic%20of%20discussion%20in%20the%20aviation%20industry%2C%20Poonam%20shares%20with%20%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Cem%3E%20%3C%2Fem%3Ethat%20pilots%20around%20the%20globe%20are%20trained%20to%20face%20all%20the%20possible%20technical%20dangers%20that%20can%20be%20imagined.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CEvery%20six%20months%2C%20pilots%20undergo%20training%20in%20a%20simulated%20setup.%20The%20process%20is%20divided%20into%20two%20days.%20On%20the%20first%20day%2C%20we%20have%20a%20four-hour%20session%2C%20and%20on%20the%20second%2C%20we%20go%20for%20checks.%20One%20of%20the%20standard%20operating%20procedures%20during%20emergencies%20for%20pilots%20is%20to%20%3Cem%3E