t%20Jet%20Airways%2C%20Captain%20Poonam%20was%20fondly%20called%20the%20%E2%80%9CGolden%20Girl%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20any%20in-flight%20emergency%2C%20there%E2%80%99s%20a%20clear%20process.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20first%20thing%20we%20do%20is%20fly%20the%20aircraft%20%E2%80%94%20stay%20in%20control%20and%20keep%20it%20steady%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20explains.%20%E2%80%9CThen%20we%20inform%20Air%20Traffic%20Control.%20After%20that%2C%20we%20follow%20a%20checklist%20from%20the%20%3Cem%3EQuick%20Reference%20Handbook%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20which%20lists%20step-by-step%20actions%20for%20different%20emergencies.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20pilot%20%E2%80%94%20usually%20the%20senior%20commander%20%E2%80%94%20focuses%20on%20flying%2C%20while%20the%20other%20reads%20the%20checklist%20aloud%20and%20handles%20communication.%20%E2%80%9CIt%E2%80%99s%20about%20staying%20calm%2C%20working%20together%2C%20and%20doing%20exactly%20what%20we%E2%80%99ve%20trained%20for%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20continues%2C%20%E2%80%9CIn%20the%20event%20of%20an%20engine%20fire%2C%20the%20flight%20crew%20promptly%20initiates%20the%20Engine%20Fire%20checklist%2C%20which%20includes%20shutting%20down%20the%20affected%20engine%20and%20discharging%20the%20onboard%20fire%20extinguishing%20agent.%20Following%20completion%20of%20the%20immediate%20actions%2C%20the%20crew%20assesses%20the%20aircraft%E2%80%99s%20condition%2C%20identifies%20the%20nearest%20suitable%20aerodrome%2C%20and%20commences%20diversion%20procedures%20for%20an%20expedited%20landing%2C%20as%20an%20engine%20fire%20is%20classified%20as%20a%20Mayday-level%20emergency.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20not%20every%20in-flight%20issue%20requires%20an%20emergency%20landing%2C%E2%80%9D%20Poonam%20explains.%20%E2%80%9CThere%20are%20also%20caution-level%20alerts%20that%20indicate%20non-critical%20system%20anomalies%2C%20allowing%20time%20for%20assessment%20and%20response.%20For%20example%2C%20if%20the%20landing%20gear%20fails%20to%20extend%20during%20the%20approach%20phase%20due%20to%20a%20hydraulic%20failure%2C%20the%20crew%20follows%20the%20Landing%20Gear%20Extension%20Failure%20checklist%20and%20uses%20the%20alternate%20system%2C%20which%20allows%20the%20gear%20to%20be%20extended%20mechanically.%20Such%20systems%20are%20built%20into%20the%20aircraft%20to%20ensure%20a%20safe%20landing%20even%20in%20the%20event%20of%20primary%20system%20failure.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20key%2C%20she%20says%2C%20is%20knowing%20which%20problems%20need%20urgent%20action%20and%20which%20ones%20give%20you%20some%20breathing%20room.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20also%20highlights%20the%20importance%20of%20Crew%20Resource%20Management%20%E2%80%94%20a%20core%20part%20of%20pilot%20training%20that%20focuses%20on%20staying%20calm%2C%20communicating%20clearly%2C%20and%20working%20together%20with%20the%20co-pilot%20and%20crew%20during%20any%20kind%20of%20technical%20fault.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EInside%20the%20cockpit%2C%20when%20systems%20fail%20and%20decisions%20can%E2%80%99t%20wait%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20so%20much%20modern%20technology%20in%20today%E2%80%99s%20aircraft%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20easy%20to%20assume%20that%20machines%20handle%20most%20things%20%E2%80%94%20even%20during%20emergencies.%20But%20what%20happens%20when%20those%20systems%20stop%20working%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FTBI-FEATURED-IMAGE-70-1752131600.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22For%20Poonam%2C%20flying%20is%20only%20part%20of%20the%20dream.%20The%20bigger%20goal%20is%20making%20space%20for%20more%20women%20in%20aviation.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FTBI-FEATURED-IMAGE-70-1752131600.jpg%2